OL,3,CKing's Christmas message reflects on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FWhen King Charles recorded his festive
OL,7,Fbroadcast in 2023, he did not know
OL,8,Fwhat awaited him and the Princess of
OL,9,FWales in the following 12 months.
OL,11,FToday, the King walked to church for
OL,12,Fthe 11 o'clock service at Sandringham
OL,13,Fas a cancer patient as his treatment
OL,14,Fcontinues into the new year.
OL,16,FKate meanwhile, walked to church hand
OL,17,Fin hand with her youngest child,
OL,18,FPrince Louis.
