OL,3,CKing's Christmas message reflects on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FSo, in his broadcast from Fitzrovia
OL,7,FChapel in central London, the former
OL,8,FMiddlesex Hospital chapel, the King
OL,9,Fmade a rare personal note, saying how
OL,10,Fthe year had been uncertain and
OL,11,Fanxious for him and his family.
OL,13,FThe chapel is now a space for those of
OL,14,Fall faiths and none, who can come to
OL,15,Fsit in the still and quiet
OL,16,Fsurroundings just steps away from
OL,17,FOxford Street.
