OL,3,CKing's Christmas message reflects on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FThe King wanted to pass his personal
OL,7,Fthanks to the doctors and nurses who
OL,8,Fhave supported him and Kate through
OL,9,Ftheir cancer treatment which had given
OL,10,Fthem "strength, care and comfort".
OL,12,FThe appreciation was also extended to
OL,13,Fthose neither of them know, who have
OL,14,Fsent messages of support and goodwill.
OL,16,FWe don't know what cancer the King has
OL,17,Fnor what treatment he is receiving,
OL,18,Fbut we do know his doctors will
OL,19,Fcontinue to manage his cancer care
OL,20,Finto 2025.
