OL,3,CKing's Christmas message reflects on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FA theme of his speech this year was
OL,7,F"listening and understanding".
OL,9,FAnd whilst he spoke about the summer
OL,10,Friots which erupted in several towns
OL,11,Fand cities following the killing of
OL,12,Fthree young girls in Southport,
OL,13,FCharles decided to focus on the unity
OL,14,Frather than the division.
OL,16,FHe spoke of how proud he had been to
OL,17,Fsee communities come together to
OL,18,F"repair" the damage rather than repeat
OL,19,Fit.
