OL,3,CKing's Christmas message reflects on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FAnd he talked about the importance of
OL,7,Frepairing relationships and trust
OL,8,Fbetween people after many days in
OL,9,Fwhich hatred had been the focus.
OL,11,FIt was also a year in which the King
OL,12,Fwas confronted with the wrongs of
OL,13,FBritish colonial rule.
OL,15,FIn October, in Australia, he met
OL,16,Findigenous people whose ancestors were
OL,17,Fmurdered and displaced following the
OL,18,Farrival of British settlers.
