OL,6,FThis is a King who has, this year,
OL,7,Fbeen hugged by women rugby players and
OL,8,Findigenous Australians alike, and
OL,9,Fafter a very difficult 2024 for him
OL,10,Fand those close to him ` King Charles,
OL,11,Fnotwithstanding his continuing health
OL,12,Fstruggles, will be hoping for a
OL,13,Fsmoother 2025.
